{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五章萧秋水当众揭发屈寒山为权力帮剑王，梁斗挺身护他并允许他说完。康出渔欲杀萧秋水灭口被梁斗拦下，屈寒山见阴谋将败，猝然偷袭梁斗。梁斗中掌受伤，但凭聪明识破屈寒山过于镇定的破绽。广东五虎醒悟后联手抗击屈寒山，权力帮主力“长天五剑”“狮公虎婆”“刀魔”杜绝等赶到增援。千钧一发之际，广西五友及时赶到。梁斗一刀斩伤屈寒山迫退权力帮。众人逃往丹霞山别传寺，途中结为兄弟。到达后梁斗遇大印法师被害的陷阱，萧秋水和罗海牛则遭遇假扮玉玺的火王。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“屈寒山，他是权力帮中的剑王，两广两湖一路的人魔，都是他联系的！四绝一君，都为他所杀；杜月山前辈，也是他囚禁的。”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你们不相信，可以检查他背门十二道要穴，‘九指神捕’胡十四曾拿住他留下指痕，……唐家唐朋也曾与之决战过，你们可以问那些人！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这康出渔是权力帮中‘无名神魔’，他杀了张临意，萧东广和唐大……！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“浣花剑派已被权力帮包围了，我们险死还生地逃出来，为的是告诉天下人这件事！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这小子信口雌黄，该杀！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "text": "“让他说下去。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“给他说下去，看他能说些什么。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这些话，显然是权力帮着他说的，来分化我们的。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“也不一定有人会教他说，希望只是误会。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这小子无凭无据，这样的谎言，也亏他说得出！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我有证据！我有证据！胡十四就在桂花轩附近！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“胡说！胡十四早已给我们……！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“梁大侠！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“屈兄，好厉害的掌法埃”",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“梁大侠，端的好内力！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“你怎么知道我要出手？！”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“你的话。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“我的话！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“你的话。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“我不相信我的话会出纰漏，我镇静得很！”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“就是因为太镇静了，”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“要不是你，又何必这样镇定呢，人被冤诬总会有些生气的。”",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“看来你是个聪明人，我只好非杀你不可了。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我若不无一点点小聪明，待你掌剑俱至时才避开去，我就没有命在了。你替我护法，我要运功调息。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他保护你？他保护得了自己就好了。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你这是闭目待毙1”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guang_dong_wu_hu_1",
      "speaker_name": "一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“谁说的？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guang_dong_wu_hu_2",
      "speaker_name": "另一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我说不是。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guang_dong_wu_hu_3",
      "speaker_name": "又一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“有我们在，梁大侠怎会有事？！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guang_dong_wu_hu_4",
      "speaker_name": "另一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“连屈大侠也不能！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guang_dong_wu_hu_5",
      "speaker_name": "还有一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“什么屈大侠，简直是屈打屁！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“在广州，我们只佩服两个人，一个是梁大侠，一个是你。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_cai",
      "speaker_name": "吴财",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“可是现在只剩下一个人了。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“难道你们不怕死吗？”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“我们广东五虎怕过什么来！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chao_yang_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "疯女",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“我们只怕仁人义士，像你这种不仁不信不忠不义之辈，我们会怕就不是人！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_shui",
      "speaker_name": "阿水",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“我们本来最敬重的就是粱大侠，不是你，只要你敢动梁大侠和萧秋水分毫，我们就跟你拼！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你们岂是我的对手！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“中国人有拳头、笔墨与志气”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“看你们往哪儿跑？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们要你们，死无葬身之地。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“就抛你们在河里喂王八好了。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不过还得先让我挑下了舌头。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这萧秋水要留给我。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我看你们这次，倒是调兵遣将想晤死都几难咯。”",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "权力帮众",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“是！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_hua",
      "speaker_name": "洪华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“谁欺负广东五虎，就等于是欺侮咱们。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yue",
      "speaker_name": "施月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“广东五虎就是广西五友的兄弟！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "劳九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们就是广西五友。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "胡福",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“梁大侠是我们恩人。”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hei",
      "speaker_name": "李黑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“谁要杀他，我们就杀谁！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“广西五友！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "null",
      "speaker_name": "广东五虎、广西五友",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“江山如画，两广豪杰！”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“格杀毋论！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他们不是退走，而是包围了我们。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“那我们该怎么办？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“逃！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“逃也是一种战略。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“正如退也是一种反击。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“屈寒山不知我已运气调息，内伤复元，中了我一刀，他要立即疗伤，故不敢恋战，所以必定会派人来盯梢。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他们是重组精兵，认准我们走投无路之时，才一举搏杀我们。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“据知权力帮‘八大天王’中，‘鬼王’也从陕西到了广西。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们必须退到一个可以无后顾之忧的地方，再图反扑。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_du_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "大肚和尚",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“那我们逃到哪里去？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“丹霞，到丹霞去。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这些人只是权力帮的小兵卒而已，屈寒山是用他们来逼我出手，看我伤势如何，再调集主力作歼灭战。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他亦受了伤，我也不知道他的伤势如何。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“大印法师这么老了，还是在烧饭；那么玉玺和尚一定在河床汲水了。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你和海牛下去招呼一声，就说梁斗回来了；”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们这就进去，大印法师是有道高僧，诸位大可随便，但不宜过于喧嚷。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "金刀胡福",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“梁大侠请放心，我们到别传寺中，自会检点便是。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“本来大家武林中人，亦不必讲较这些繁文褥节。大印法师武功亦颇深湛，经学渊博，但寺中常住有读书秀才，他们在此结庐苦读，且有掸宗饱学之士在此，不得不迁就一二。请位当然知道，这些前龙图学士，最好还是不惹为妙。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“也不知皇帝豢养这些所谓饱学之士，有什么因由！这些人大都是愿降求和之辈，与敌军鏖战未竟，他们已吓得屁滚尿流了。”",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "“自古良药苦口，忠臣剖心，算了吧，听说大侠梁斗曾在别传寺盘桓甚久，皆因两位方外之交，一是大印法师，另一就是这位玉玺，我们还是下去招呼一声吧。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“暧，你既未识梁大侠在先，又何从得知这些？怎么我不知道的。”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "“消息来源，一是江湖传言，一是典籍所载，我就是从书本上得知的。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "speaker_name": "罗海牛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“哦，梁大侠的生平事迹，已记在书籍之上了？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_luo_hai_niu",
      "text": "“梁大侠年少时行侠仗义的轶事，早已记入史册之中，以及日后江湖后辈的心中了。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你们请坐，我进去招呼主持一声，再给你们安排香客房。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“雍学士，史记之后，可又穷研什么高深学问？”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“现攻汉书，史记毕竟谬言测度颇多，不如汉书乃金石之文，正气之言，不愧为儒者之法制！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“怎么？你这两广名侠，到江湖去溜了个圈，又回来净禅么？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“回来跟学士请教学问。向法师间经，跟玉奎对弃。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“读书么？弟可奉陪！现下大印在厨煮斋，玉玺在溪边……”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“待我煮水热茶，再跟诸位论道。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "金刀胡福",
      "listener": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "text": "“学士盛意拳拳，弟等甚感——”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hei",
      "speaker_name": "铁钉李黑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“哈！我正是口渴！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_zai",
      "speaker_name": "杀仔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好哇，你冲茶，我一定喝！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我去厨房拜谒一位旧交，你们就在此地，‘陪’雍学士饮茶吧。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chao_yang_feng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "疯女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“怎么茶壶这样小，才不够我们喝哩。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yong_xi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "雍希羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这些人，真糟塌了我的好茶叶，我的好茶壶！”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_da_yin",
      "text": "“主持。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_da_yin",
      "text": "“大樱”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 5
    }
  ],
